  "remarks": "\nSouthFront is a website which has spread disinformation relating to Ukraine and promoted the Government of Russia’s false narrative about the Russian invasion of Ukraine. SouthFront has therefore supported and promoted policies and activities which destabilise Ukraine and undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
